_sText:
A custom jailbreak map originally created by Semicolon backslash for a team fortress 2, 72-hour winter jam. and was updated after a while. The CSS port of this map is heavily edited and features an extended layout, more games, and reworked a few games to add more twists and features. A vent system, guns, and teleports have been set in place to ensure a smooth rebel experience, while also adding more options for CTs. 

A full list of the map features is included here:

1- Deathcrate
2- Dodgeball
3- Jumprope
4- Deathrun
5- Obstacle Course
6- Wrecking Ball
7- Box Game
8- Wall Runners
9- Crush Game 
10- Coloring Clash
11- Sweeper
12- Jump Rope
13- Cracker Barrel
14- Jeopardy
15- Sports
16- Arena
17- Spleef
18- Disco
19- Forklift
20- Spleef
- And a few secrets Teleports, Guns & forklifts, Enjoy the map!
